- All code comments should be written in Simplified Chinese to make it easier for users to understand
- However, the code itself (variable names, function names, class names, etc.) should remain in English, following the project's naming conventions
- Project documentation (such as README, API documentation, etc.) should be written in English to maintain professionalism and internationalization

In summary: All communication with users should be in Chinese, while code structure and project documentation should remain in English.
